item.title: Project 1: Techionista Holiday
item.description: Techionista Holiday is a e-commerce company for travelling. Techionista Holiday’s mission is to make it easy for travellers to organize the perfect trip. On their website, you can book hotel rooms, apartments and other unique stays. As a traveller, you can give reviews and comments on your stay. Assignment: Techionista Holiday managers would love to gain more insight into different types of travelers and their feedback. These valuable insights can help them improve Techionista Holiday’s website and their capability of catering to their users’ needs.
